FBIS3-23492 "jptot013__l94020" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 24 March 1994 EAST EUROPE ALBANIA `Unknown Persons' Plant Bombs in Homes of Reformists AU2403122494 Tirana ATA in English 1129 GMT 24 Mar 94 AU2403122494 Tirana ATA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Tirana, March 24 (ATA) -- Unknown persons have put explosives into several houses of the former politically persecuted who have taken part in the democratic changes. Bashkim Kodhima, head of the Association Former Political Persecuted of the Saranda district branch, and Minella Boci, the head of the former economically persecuted and kulaks of the district, issued yesterday a protest note addressed to the Ministry of Public Order, Ministry of Justice, the National Information Service (SHIK), through which they urge to find the terrorists. Mr. Kodhima and Mr. Boci blame leftist extremists to have done this act.
